Package clientGUI

Class CeoGUIController

  • java.lang.Object
    • clientGUI.CeoGUIController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable
    public class CeoGUIController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    CeoGUIController class is responsible for allowing the CEO pick a desired action by clicking a button, either viewing specific shop reports or viewing annual report, both of the buttons will direct the CEO to new GUI.

    Project Name: Zer-Li (Flowers store in Java)

    Version:
    V1.00 2022
    Author:
    Habib Ibrahim, Vitaly Rofman, Ibrahim Daoud, Yosif Hosen
